name: Roy Tang
text: parang wala akong sinabing "longer"  :p  Roxas has a more solid record with no corruption allegations anywhere, while Binay is often the subject of such allegations and of course is a crony of Erap. I cannot in good faith support anyone who thinks it was a good idea for Erap to run for president again.
